                             'Blokator' 1.01

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Blokator' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you 'drop' blocks of
various shapes and colours so they are placed next to blocks of
the same type and/or colour. When blocks can no longer be put on
the game board, the board is then 'cleaned-up', that is, the
'associated' blocks are removed and the game continues...

  Have fun!

